{"tid":1281842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Now專訪】曾鈺成：可考慮831框架外討論重啟政改","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T12:20:00.000Z","uid":68860,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f12d1f6ef29825e3ae17ac79eaa7e85311df8f08","tid":1281842,"uid":68860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gor2Y29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGor2Y29.png&h=42e70eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】前立法會主席曾鈺成接受本台專訪，他認為修例風波其中一個主因是香港一直未落實普選，令社會怨氣愈積愈大，他提出在831框架以外，討論重啟政改。他又認為，反修例衝突中多人被捕，行政長官可考慮特赦。<br />\n<br />\n立法會大樓被衝擊，回歸後歷任主席的相無一倖免，但曾鈺成的相並非第一個遭殃。大樓變得滿目瘡痍，曾鈺成形容自己當晚欲哭無淚。<br />\n<br />\n多次衝突，被捕的主要是年輕人，曾鈺成認為經法庭審訊後，特首可以考慮特赦。<br />\n<br />\n風波持續多月，曾鈺成認為問題徵結在於香港一直未落實普選，令民怨累積。他建議在不受制於831決定下，討論重啟政改。<br />\n<br />\n他支持林鄭月娥繼續留任，但希望她在10月的施政報告，大刀闊斧提出解決民生問題的措施，紓緩貧富懸殊等社會不公義。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=354086&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D354086%26refer%3D&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=bac3c5d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D354086%26refer%3D&h=41b55c7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=354086&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"ebc038200d403d5c0d72289f7ff0c4330f810ba4","tid":1281842,"uid":248404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"會特赦先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72867002273336fbc8df97933ce37e6d907088cc","tid":1281842,"uid":68860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:43:44.000Z","msg":"曾鈺成幫大家探緊口風"},{"pid":"47dab0f7d04eeb491806d90a00c937ac495a92b3","tid":1281842,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72867002273336fbc8df97933